Package: maldiscrim
Title: Analysis and Discrimination of MALDI-TOF Mass Spectra
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Stowe", "AGBESSI", "Paul Marie", "GROLLEMUND", , "agb.stowe@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for the processing and discriminant analysis of MALDI-TOF mass spectra. 
    The package implements functional data analysis techniques, specifically Functional Partial Least Squares - 
    Discriminant Analysis (FPLS-DA), and deep learning methods via Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN). It includes 
    spectral transformations using B-Spline basis functions and wavelets for dimension reduction and smoothing. 
    Functions are provided for spectra data import, preprocessing, model training, prediction, and graphical visualizations. 
